title: 820-00244: No booting up
message:
I have this board that doesn't seem to boot up.  PM_PCH_PWROK is 3.3 so is PP5V_S0 @ 5. I've connected external display with no output and the board is warm to the touch after a few minutes. The battery also charges. 

Any suggestions on what to check next?

title: 820-00244: No booting up
message:
Check if you get VCORE and voltage on other coils too.
You know, A1534 are known for CPU dying very easy.
Be aware of losing time...
